And yeah, having a bit of a pool to dip into from other trades is a definite help. If it hadn't been for my brewing profits I probably would never have dared enter the realm of tinkering. Takes the edge off of those 1k combines to know you can always go back to your day job of keeping Norrath fat and drunk.
<br />

<br />
Although I've noticed I'm now selling a decent amount of the LoY geerloks since not many people seem to be making them on my server, good deal of lucin ones up for sale but much less LoY ones - and when they do make the LoY they only seem to do the quills. So I'll probably save more of those to bazaar sell as I skill up on them. I'm also hoping to sell a few more geerloks once the new tradeskill system goes live and have set aside some for that.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
